title: Exception throws when export data from table containing highlight/map.
description:
Description: When exporting data from the attached report, an exception is thrown. Steps to reproduce: 
1. Add a table which has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the report attached.
3. Export the data in the table.
OB: An exception is thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight and map rules in the group row.
EB: When exporting data from a table containing highlight and map rules in the group row, the data should be exported without any exceptions.
SR:
1. Add a table which has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the report attached.
3. Export the data in the table.
